WARNING:

1.Make sure you have installed all kinds of drivers for your device!
2.Make sure your phone has connected to your PC via USB cable!
3.Make sure you have turned off USB-Storage Mode!
4.DO NOT Plug Out USB cable during Flashing!
5.The program will automatically flash the kernel provided in BlendMIUI-kernel directory for your device.However you can replace the boot.img by other's if you like.
6.Report bugs with screenshot to JasonStein@live.cn.

Press any key to start Auto-Flash!